articularly in patients with advanced age and/or renal impairment.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/190550/', '', 'Liraglutide, Lixisenatide', 'Acetaminophen, Ziconotide, Methoxyflurane', 1767369485);
